data.text: Old Master, British and European Art Tuesday 25 June 2024 | 10am London Viewing | Highlights A selection of lots will be on view Thursday 6 - Thursday 13 June at our London Gallery, 15 Cecil Court, London WC2N 4EZ, as follows: Monday-Friday, 11.30am - 5.30pm For more information, please contact 0203 971 2500 | london@sworder.co.uk Stansted Viewing | Auction Viewing will be held at our Stansted Auction Rooms, Cambridge Road, Stansted Mountfitchet CM24 8GE, as follows: Friday 21 June, 10am - 4pm Sunday 23 June, 10am - 1pm Monday 24 June, 10am - 4pm The auction will take place at our Stansted Auction Rooms, Cambridge Road, Stansted Mountfitchet CM24 8GE.
